SUMMARY:Deadline: Festival SCAN: 4a Residència de Creació i Investigació
  at L'Arxiu Tarragona
DESCRIPTION:Residency call for artists\, researchers and curators to develo
 p artistic or research projects around archival photographic and audiovisu
 al media at the Centre d'Imatges de Tarragona. Selected applicants receive
  €900 in project support\, free accommodation for up to 5 days\, and acc
 ess to a 1.5 million-strong archive. Resulting work must be publicly prese
 nted in November 2026 in a format of the artist's choosing.\n\nOrganisatio
 n: Festival SCAN & Centre d'Imatges de Tarragona / L'Arxiu\nLocation: Tarr
 agona\, Spain\nAward: €900 + 5 nights free accommodation + access to 1.5
